同燉奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紅豆沙就一時時<br />\n燉奶凍咗都ok喎<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲野食係熱食好食，雪凍都好食<br />\n唔熱唔凍暖暖地嗰陣就好撚難食<br />\n例如中式糖水<br />\n<br />\nBetween布甸熱食是咪即係燉蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87fd5ced4bb095619295b3d14fecec5d9185aa70","tid":95150,"uid":73689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:27:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>火鍋都唔同打邊爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁其實講到打邊爐既書面語未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔通寫文寫信照寫打邊爐？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20070118000051KK01256\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.answers.yahoo.com%2Fquestion%2Findex%3Fqid%3D20070118000051KK01256&d=RBEWNUJz0QdmPTNU9652XEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=3808178e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20070118000051KK01256</a><br />\n<br />\n文盲係用黎教化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>以後上連登唔比用書面語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家唔好當廣東話就唔可以寫底，難登大雅之堂。其實，大中華各地都有地方用詞，中港台嘅所謂書面語都有區分。所以，要敢於用自己嘅語言講，用自己嘅語言寫。香港人都可以<del>「我手寫我口」</del>講咩就寫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd915de6bb827c44b860d1eb3e5468cf295a8546","tid":95150,"uid":47613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:28:30.000Z","msg":"雞煲"},{"pid":"ea250a83cb4625ec5bc6bc2151a655fa6c23f436","tid":95150,"uid":16239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:50:01.000Z","msg":"燒味"},{"pid":"c184fb4622085a25912e72ac5fc25abed8454571","tid":95150,"uid":4730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>羅漢果水呢類苦野，一凍左完全擺唔落口</blockquote><br />\n甜㗎啵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我特登雪凍冇咁甜嚟飲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d00308f9b73bb08b73e3d1ad9a3876ecf6d95903","tid":95150,"uid":8174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T05:53:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>油炸食物</blockquote><br />\n啲炸野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔准講書面語嫁連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}